So it calls `simplifyInstructionWithOperands` with the new operands. `simplifyInstructionWithOperands` should simplify `icmp eq X, X` to true regardless of what `X` is. Let me check if maybe the issue is with `PreventSelfSimplify`:

```cpp
auto PreventSelfSimplify = [V](Value *Simplified) {
